{"tid":1142184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【涉妨礙司法公正】近400前檢察官聯署 指特朗普如非總統早已被起訴","createTime":"2019-05-07T02:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T02:27:16.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc332f38c317e776633c89d32bacfbe57c033b3","tid":1142184,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557176455_d471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557176455_d471.jpg&h=f29001a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近400名前檢察官認為，特朗普如非總統，早已被控妨礙司法公正。(資料圖片)<br />\n美國近400位前聯邦檢察官聯署，認為總統特朗普如果不是在任，早已被控妨礙司法公正。<br />\n<br />\n反特朗普的非牟利組織「保護民主」（Protect Democracy）公開那封聯署信，有份簽名的前檢察官都曾在民主黨和共和黨政府工作。<br />\n<br />\n特別檢察官米勒（Robert Mueller）的「通俄門」調查報告上月公開。司法部長巴爾（William Barr）指米勒在報告列出特朗普涉妨礙調查的十件事件，評估是否構成妨礙司法公正，米勒本身未有定論，但巴爾和羅森斯坦都不同意米勒的一些法律觀點，認為米勒沒有「足夠證據」斷定特朗普犯妨礙司法公正罪。<br />\n<br />\n司法部的政策是不起訴在任總統。<br />\n<br />\n米勒沒有足夠證據指控特朗普妨礙司法公正，但米勒團隊在報告披露特朗普曾試圖炒掉他，指國會仍有權對特朗普採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190507/59571777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59571777&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=cafc4d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59571777&h=f6fde04a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190507/59571777</a>"},{"pid":"c8ba5d571ff3823793beb948457560f3028f5131","tid":1142184,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"炒咗先係妨礙司法公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}